snippet: The Jets downgraded the status of Wilkerson from doubtful to out and said he would not travel to Tennessee for Sunday’s game.
abstract: New York Jets defensive end Muhammad Wilkerson will not play in upcoming game against Tennessee Titans.
lead_paragraph: The Jets downgraded the status of Wilkerson from doubtful to out and said he would not travel to Tennessee for Sunday’s game.

headline.main: Jets’ Muhammad Wilkerson Won’t Play Against Titans
headline.print_headline: Jets’ Wilkerson Won’t Play Against Titans
